sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects potentially suspicious keywords that could indicate the use of a PowerShell exploitation framework
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Perez Diego (@darkquassar), Tuan Le (NCSGroup)

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects execution of "aspnet_compiler.exe" which can be abused to compile and execute C# code.
Get the processes that are running on the local computer.

attributes.magic: ASCII text, with very long lines (65400u), with CRLF line terminators

threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered trojan. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET MALWARE AgentTesla Exfil Via SMTP
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw:
alert smtp $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE AgentTesla Exfil Via SMTP"; flow:established,to_server; content:"|0d 0a|Time|3a 20|"; content:"
User Name|3a 20|"; distance:0; content:"
OSFullName|3a 20|"; distance:0; fast_pattern; reference:md5,b8b71fc1124765b75b3aa3be805e9d12; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2030171; rev:1; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, created_at 2020_05_18, deployment Perimeter, malware_family AgentTesla, confidence High, signature_severity Major, updated_at 2020_05_18;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET MALWARE Agent Tesla CnC Exfil via TCP
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp-pkt $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET MALWARE Agent Tesla CnC Exfil via TCP"; flow:established,to_server; content:"Time|3a 20|"; startswith; content:"|3c|br|3e|User|20|Name|3a 20|"; distance:19; within:15; content:"|3c|br|3e|Computer|20|Name|3a 20|"; distance:0; content:"|3c|br|3e|OSFullName|3a 20|"; distance:0; fast_pattern; content:"|3c|br|3e|Password|3a 20|"; content:"|3c|br|3e 3c|hr|3e|"; endswith; reference:md5,f1b1fdd112b02733cd8e5d8ed62acec1; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:2063399; rev:1; metadata:affected_product Windows_XP_Vista_7_8_10_Server_32_64_Bit, attack_target Client_Endpoint, tls_state plaintext, created_at 2025_07_10, deployment Perimeter, malware_family AgentTesla, confidence High, signature_severity Critical, updated_at 2025_07_10; target:src_ip;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: SURICATA Applayer Detect protocol only one direction
